media:group.media:description:
Thanks to SCREEN JUNKIES for helping out with this 300th Episode of Pitch Meeting! Subscribe to them and watch a million Honest Trailers right here: https://www.youtube.com/c/screenjunkies

Subscribe to THIS CHANNEL for more Pitch Meetings: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9Kq-yEt1iYsbUzNOoIRK0g

It’s the team-up crossover episode you never knew you wanted. Or maybe you didn’t want it at all. Anyway, you’re getting it. Screen Junkies and Epic Voice Guy team up with Ryan George and Screenwriter Guy and Producer guy to make a crazy collaboration of two of the most popular “let’s make fun of movies but in kind of a loving way” channels on YouTube.

Did we just create a cinematic universe? Maybe. Who's to say?
